@ kei82
1. Install Office.
2. Open any Office app. like Word 2013
3. When its opened for the first time Activate Office window opens.
4. Click on Enter a product key instead.
5. Now enter the key and press continue.
6. Select the option of phone activation.
7. Select your country and dial the mentioned number using phone or skype.
8. Follow the procedure and fill the Confirmation ID and press next to finish the activation.
9. Enjoy your pirated copy of Office 2013;-)

@ kei82
To easy change keys in Office 2013, Run Command Prompt (CMD) as Admin and enter the following:
For x86: cscript "C:Program FilesMicrosoft OfficeOffice15ospp.vbs" /inpkey:XXXXX-XXXXX-XXXXX-XXXXX-RCXKK
For x64: cscript "C:Program Files (x86)Microsoft OfficeOffice15ospp.vbs" /inpkey:XXXXX-XXXXX-XXXXX-XXXXX-RCXKK
NOTE: If you liked the software then please purchase it to support its developers!

@SynisterSilence, Explore your program files at c drive, look at the path, there should be microsoft office folder, inside the folder you will find office15 folder that contain ospp.vbs visual basic script.
Now open command prompt as admin, type: cd c:Program FilesMicrosoft OfficeOffice15 and press enter
continue type: cscript ospp.vbs inpkey:xxxx-xxxx-xxx
make sure you type it correctly
you need to add backslash after the colon and the folder. the comment here disable that \ symbol
